        "action": "Make the use of mobile phones while driving an instant driving ban.",
        "additional_details": "I  firmly believe that a three month driving ban would help greatly stop drivers using phones as they drive.making it difficult to get to work without a car . If  put in this position then it will make them think before using the phone while driving.",
        "background": "As an approved driving instructor Every day i see drivers using their phones Clearly the 6 points and \u00a3200 fine have not had the desired effect to make people stop using phones while driving\r\nI firmly believe that a three month driving ban would help greatly stop drivers using phones as they drive",
